@startuml 04_state_machine
title 実行状態の遷移
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans CJK JP"
skinparam shadowing false

state "未実行 (Idle)" as Idle
state "実行中 (Running)" as Running
state "再開待ち (Waiting)" as Waiting

[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Running : startTransfer() /\nstartTransferAllOwned()
Running --> Waiting : 制限時間が近づいた\n(状態保存 + トリガー予約)
Waiting --> Running : 約 60 秒後に\nresumeTransfer() が自動起動
Running --> Idle : 全件処理完了\n(状態クリア + トリガー削除)
Running --> Idle : stopTransfer()\n(手動リセット)
Waiting --> Idle : stopTransfer()\n(手動リセット)
@enduml
